HEADWORD: Polytungstic
<hw>Pol`y*tung"stic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Containing several tungsten atoms or radicals; <as>as,
<ex>polytungstic</ex> acid</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Polytungstic acid</b></col> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>, <cd>any
one of several complex acids of tungsten containing more than one atom
of tungsten.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polytype</ent>⟦br⟧
